{"tid":755272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好可恨，姓李果家人出到天災氣候力場 !","createTime":"2018-07-25T05:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T05:52:46.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"103b17a16cf41d25b5643c09a9ee19314ef31f38","tid":755272,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:43:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180725/58483051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58483051&d=6VBb3GZXc6PsEmgOQRdGZ0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=c20d3eb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180725%2F58483051&h=ac47ab82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180725/58483051</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全個北半球</span>熱浪迫人，歐洲及亞洲各地都錄得破紀錄高溫，酷熱天氣至今已造成多人身亡。世界氣象組織（World Meteorological Organization）周二發表聲明指，夏天才過一半，但溫度破紀錄、熱浪、乾旱和暴雨等極端天氣在北半球肆虐，對人類健康、農業、生態系統、基礎建設皆有廣泛影響，酷熱更會引致災難性的山火。<br />\n<br />\n希臘的氣溫升至40℃以上，引發嚴重山火，造成至少74人死亡，超過1,200間房屋損毀。總理齊普拉斯宣佈，全國為死難者哀悼3日。意大利西西里也發生多宗山火。<br />\n瑞典錄得有史以來最高溫的7月，引發大型山火。當地農民指部分地區5月以來就持續乾旱，可能會造成糧食短缺，預計今年的糧食收成是25年來最差，有奶農更被逼屠宰牲口。<br />\n英國本周的氣溫預期會升至38.5℃新高，當地氣象部門之前已發出多次酷熱及曝曬警告，周二表示英國錄得連續54日的乾旱天氣，降雨稀少。<br />\n美國加州7月中以來發生嚴重山火，加州塞拉國家森林（Sierra National Forests）山火的受災範圍達1.5萬公頃土地，當局派出3,300名救援人員撲救，行動導致消防員1死6傷。加州優勝美地國家公園（Yosemite National Park）亦受到這場山火威脅，周三下午起局部關閉，逾千營地及酒店預約要取消。<br />\n在日本，本周的熱浪已導致至少14人死亡，部分地區氣溫高逾40℃，埼玉縣熊谷市氣溫錄得41.1℃破紀錄新高。當地政府會正式列酷暑為自然災害之一。<br />\n南韓的永川巿在24日錄得40.3℃，是1942年以來的最高溫度。<br />\n<br />\n香港明明係北半球，竟然就係小小一個地方無事。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752eb3546bbddd414c69467daff0d23661b82da8","tid":755272,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"香港濕熱世界第一你無聽過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a47303217cb9506e14b1bdbdadd384fff0ed93","tid":755272,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"752eb3546bbddd414c69467daff0d23661b82da8","tid":755272,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"香港濕熱世界第一你無聽過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"無過佰人濕熱死。。。唔公平"},{"pid":"7078b735b3065a45157469ab7edff1680a9de0e5","tid":755272,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:48:25.000Z","msg":"一次又一次可以富財重新分配，就係比李家搞衰哂。。。"},{"pid":"30825490be28b7aeed3f23622d37bcec2ff6544a","tid":755272,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/134836_453a346c69b1f632561da1eb71926c73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F134836_453a346c69b1f632561da1eb71926c73.png&h=8a96a648&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d3c77e18f98ccef5ee7abf3d00e8e1a7f0e9e9b","tid":755272,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}